WEBVTT

00:02:30.542 --> 00:02:35.083
I've devoted my career
to studying and solving this problem.

00:02:36.500 --> 00:02:38.018
For 100 years,

00:02:38.042 --> 00:02:41.976
we've used chemicals as drugs
to treat infections.

00:02:42.000 --> 00:02:44.875
Chemicals will never mutate or transmit.

00:02:46.083 --> 00:02:50.875
Similarly, our vaccines are not designed
to mutate or transmit.

00:02:52.958 --> 00:02:54.976
20 years ago,

00:02:55.000 --> 00:02:56.976
I had a radical idea

00:02:57.000 --> 00:03:01.893
to use the viruses
themselves as therapies --